main event: A circular metallic object was observed hovering over Surabaja, Indonesia by U.S. Naval Forces, accelerated to high speed, and disappeared after approximately 40 minutes.
interesting points: The object was circular and metallic, It was estimated to be 30 to 35 feet in diameter, A hazy vapor was observed emanating from the object, The sighting was authenticated by high-caliber personnel, Other reports corroborated this incident.
witness description: personnel of the U.S. Naval Forces
